{"data":[{"date":"19:21 24/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 24/6: MU chi 196 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/11/diem-tin-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU chi 196 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 246 MU chi 196 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 246 MU chi 196 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/diem-tin-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi 166 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Mirror, MU t\u00ednh chi 196 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Kylian Mbappe v\u00e0 Jose Gaya \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Mourinho nh\u1eafm Mbappe thay Martial c\u00f2n Jose Gaya \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm khi m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alex Sandro t\u1eeb Juventus \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\"Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018\"</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0110T Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG h\u1ecfi mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Le Parisien \u0111\u01b0a tin, Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea, c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\">Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span><br>\r\nReal, Barca v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barcelona s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Yerry Mina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ochoa l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ochoa noi ve tran Duc vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"Ochoa n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/thu-mon-ochoa-len-tieng-truoc-chien-thang-cua-duc-truoc-thuy-dien.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ochoa n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Guillermo Ochoa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Mexico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-ochoa-len-tieng-truoc-chien-thang-cua-duc-truoc-thuy-dien-421-189424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thu-mon-ochoa-len-tieng-truoc-chien-thang-cua-duc-truoc-thuy-dien.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thu-mon-ochoa-len-tieng-truoc-chien-thang-cua-duc-truoc-thuy-dien-421-189424.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ochoa l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span><br>\r\nGuillermo Ochoa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Mexico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua De Ligt v\u00e0 Godin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gazzetta dello Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Medhi Benatia v\u00e0 Daniele Rugani ra \u0111i, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Matthijs de Ligt c\u1ee7a Ajax v\u00e0 Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 William Carvalho</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">William Carvalho b\u1ecb Sporting ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 Inter Milan \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, hi\u1ec7n Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Loftus-Cheek v\u00e0 Wilshere</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere\" title=\"Wilshere\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Mesut-Ozil-muon-ao-so-10-cua-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Wilshere</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Everton \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Jack WIlshere v\u00e0 Ruben Loftus-Cheek. Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Arsenal theo d\u1ea1ng\u00a0chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Loftus-Cheek \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool chi 180 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Marco Asensio</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mundo Deportivo, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n chi 180 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Marco Asensio c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 700 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3802","checkdouble":"189427"},{"date":"19:59 24/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! Ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/day-nguoi-giup-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Shkodran Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bernd Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bernd Leno c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn trong khung g\u1ed7. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi C\u1ed9ng H\u00f2a S\u00e9c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua. Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 David Ospina, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Shkodran Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bernd Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Shkodran Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bernd Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Shkodran-Mustafi-thuyet-phuc-Bernd-Leno-toi-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay khi HLV Unai Emery c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Emirates \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/clb-arsenal-chinh-thuc-trinh-lang-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-172-188980.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen</span>.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Leno duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shkodran Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bernd Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mustafi thuyet phuc Bernd Leno toi Arsenal\" title=\"Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bernd Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/day-nguoi-giup-arsenal-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mustafi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bernd Leno t\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Emirates, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi \u00fd ki\u1ebfn Mustafi v\u00e0\u00a0Ozil, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u khuy\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMustafi \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t t\u1eadn t\u00ecnh, anh \u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n khuy\u00ean t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, anh \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf s\u00e2n Emirates. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 Mustafi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb \u1edf \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1eeb anh \u1ea5y. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian suy ngh\u0129 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArsenal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng NHM cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Arsenal thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3801","checkdouble":"189428"},{"date":"20:11 24/06","title":"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London, b\u1edfi v\u1eady The Blues mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Maurizio-Sarri-muon-Chelsea-mua-Alisson-voi-gia-70-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u1ebfu The Blues cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ramos-va-ronaldo-muon-real-mua-thu-mon-cua-chelsea-180-181590.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Real \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m Thibaut Courtois</span>, nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Courtois v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i TBN \u0111o\u00e0n t\u1ee5 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu thay v\u00ec k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Chelsea.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Chelsea c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n Courtois, b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Liverpool-muon-mua-Nick-Pope-cua-Burnley-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 fan cu\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Chelsea chi t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua Alisson s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ederson c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3800","checkdouble":"189429"},{"date":"21:08 24/06","title":"M.U t\u00ednh chi 30 tri\u1ec7u cho truy\u1ec1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ashley Young","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/16/mu-nham-gaya-thay-young.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf Ashley Young trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>M.U theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jose Gaya \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ashley Young</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jose Gaya \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ashley Young h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jose Gaya \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ashley Young h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/MU-theo-duoi-Jose-Gaya-de-thay-the-Ashley-Young-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jose Gaya thay Young</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ashley Young l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng v\u00ec l\u00fd do tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Young.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, M.U \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alex Sandro c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi Juventus\u00a0kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u2018h\u00e9t gi\u00e1\u2019 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u00edt ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb Jose Luis Gaya c\u1ee7a CLB Valencia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 M.U theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jose Gaya b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng. Anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng, \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. C\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Gaya khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jordi Alba, m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Valencia v\u00e0 \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi 24 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Jose Gaya \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Castellon su\u1ed1t 4 n\u0103m qua. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh ra s\u00e2n 27 tr\u1eadn cho Valencia t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho M.U trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3799","checkdouble":"189434"},{"date":"11:05 24/06","title":"Danh t\u00ednh thi\u1ebfu n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i xem World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/danh-tinh-thieu-nu-viet-ngoi-tren-khan-dai-xem-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> Thu Giang sinh n\u0103m 1999 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6-7 n\u0103m s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Moscow, Nga. \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng xem World Cup l\u00e0 v\u00ec h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo (CR7) \u0111\u1ea5y!</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn Nga xem World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn 4 n\u0103m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i quy t\u1ee5 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a l\u00e0ng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay do c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9!\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/347066652179219475648897388508714232971264n-15296781104211462792631.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/346956362076075731983535330621448803319808n-15296781072881847750530.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda, d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd xen l\u1eabn th\u00edch th\u00fa tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t c\u00f4 b\u1ea1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam xinh x\u1eafn ng\u1ed3i xem tr\u1eadn b\u00f3ng di\u1ec5n ra trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Luzhniki, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Moscow, Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn xu\u00fdt xoa ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 xen l\u1eabn ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi c\u00f4 b\u1ea1n may m\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e2n t\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i l\u00e2u, danh t\u00ednh fan girl xinh \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4 b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 B\u00f9i Thu Giang (sinh n\u0103m 1999, t\u1ea1i H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng). Giang v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang Moscow, Nga sinh s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ea7n 6,7 n\u0103m. V\u00ec r\u1ea5t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Cristiano Ronaldo (CR7) n\u00ean Giang v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft mua v\u00e9 \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng xem b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Morocco di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m 20/6 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;M\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n xem anh R\u00f4 \u1edf ngo\u00e0i n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5y. M\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 l\u00e0 bao nhi\u00eau v\u00ec b\u1ed1 m\u00ecnh mua cho c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 xem. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn qua m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh. M\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1&quot;, Giang chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xinh x\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u00f4 b\u1ea1n may m\u1eafn th\u1ea5y Cristiano Ronaldo (CR7) ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem anh \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/174387762405090197469484315349707548262400n-15296783375681356234144.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/165851944310055005679064499210570225942528n-15296783284751711308436.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/155348572478935623013138984872593102209024n-15296783477231241622257.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3798","checkdouble":"189413"},{"date":"11:12 24/06","title":"MU quy\u1ec7t chi 166 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/mu-quyet-chi-166-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Anthony Martial r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Nga d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe thay Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe thay Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/MU-muon-mua-Kylian-Mbappe-thay-Anthony-Martial-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, khi Mourinho l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Sanchez \u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean Rashford h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Monaco. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean anh \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Philippe Lamboley kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-tien-dao-martial-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-mu-172-188440.html\" target=\"_blank\">Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i suy ngh\u0129, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean r\u1eddi M.U. Martial n\u0103m nay 23 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU mua Mbappe thay Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf. MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Anthony Martial r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Mbappe thay Martial\" title=\"MU mua Mbappe thay Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/mu-quyet-chi-166-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua Mbappe thay Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Hi\u1ec7n PSG \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y PSG \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi \u0111\u1eadm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh do UEFA quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi PSG c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Neymar nh\u01b0ng Mbappe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 166 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sunday Mirror, MU th\u1eadm ch\u00ed d\u00f9ng Martial c\u1ed9ng 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 PSG s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Martial trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3797","checkdouble":"189412"},{"date":"11:36 24/06","title":"Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/6/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N'Golo Kante duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Real,-Barca-va-PSG-muon-dua-tien-ve-Kante-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Kante c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng minh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Kante c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap Les Bleus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua NGolo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLe Parisien kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/psg-chi-so-tien-sieu-khung-mua-sao-chelsea-172-188620.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Kante</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Antero Henrique c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kante, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021, The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Kante, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3796","checkdouble":"189414"},{"date":"07:19 24/06","title":"HLV Joachim Loew l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y b\u00e3o khi t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n \u0103n ... r\u1ec9 m\u0169i","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-joachim-loew-lai-gay-bao-khi-tai-hien-man-an-ri-mui.JPG","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3795","checkdouble":"189386"},{"date":"08:48 24/06","title":"Fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed v\u00ec Argentina thua th\u1ea3m","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/fan-messi-tu-tu-vi-argentina-thua-tham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t fan cu\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Messi t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 b\u1ecb nghi nh\u1ea3y s\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 t\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00e1 y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u00e0 mong manh.\r\n</h2><h2>Bi k\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a fan Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u fan tan n\u00e1t c\u00f5i l\u00f2ng khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ru\u1ed9t Argentina thua s\u1ed1c Croatia 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. C\u00f3 fan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft s\u1ed1ng n\u1eefa. Bi k\u1ecbch \u1ea5y mang t\u00ean Dinu Alex.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/nhay-song.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 cho hay Alex \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf nh\u00e0 \u0111i sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t m\u1ec7nh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nghi ng\u1edd anh ch\u00e0ng 30 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf bang Kerala c\u1ee7a \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u1eed b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch nh\u1ea3y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00f4ng Meenachil. Nguy\u00ean do khi\u1ebfn Alex ch\u00e1n \u0111\u1eddi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Messi v\u00e0 Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng Alex l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean k\u1ebf to\u00e1n \u00edt giao du b\u1ea1n b\u00e8. Anh coi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui, l\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho Messi l\u00e0 l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng. Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed1n s\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Alex vi\u1ebft: \u201cMessi, cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho anh, t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd xem anh n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\u201d. Trong cu\u1ed1n s\u1ed5 kh\u00e1c, Alex vi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00f4i y\u00eau m\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u1edf hy v\u1ecdng vinh quang. H\u00e3y ch\u1edf theo c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex c\u1ed5 v\u0169 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho Messi v\u00e0 Argentina trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Croatia. Anh c\u00f2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1eafc nh\u01b0 \u0111inh \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1ed9t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec Messi c\u0169ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec Argentina c\u0169ng th\u1eafng. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua th\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Messi v\u00e0 Argentina khi\u1ebfn Alex suy s\u1ee5p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. Anh kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft \u0103n u\u1ed1ng, kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ai n\u1eefa. B\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Alex k\u1ec3 con trai \u00f4ng l\u00ean gi\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i ng\u1ee7 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 23h30. \u0110\u1ebfn 4h30 s\u00e1ng, m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Alex th\u1ea5y ph\u00f2ng con trai v\u1eabn s\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e8n m\u1edbi sang xem th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y anh \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 Alex \u0111i\u1ebfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t m\u1ec7nh anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i: \u201cV\u1edbi t\u00f4i, th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u00fd ngh\u0129a n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft cho m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e2y. Kh\u00f4ng ai ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m g\u00ec v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u1ea3\u201d. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u00e1 th\u01b0 tuy\u1ec7t m\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc \u1ed1p l\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f3 in h\u00ecnh Messi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia \u0111\u00ecnh Alex h\u1ed1t ho\u1ea3ng b\u00e1o c\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t. Ch\u00f3 nghi\u1ec7p v\u1ee5 sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh h\u01a1i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Alex \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i ra ph\u00eda s\u00f4ng Meenachil th\u00ec d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, m\u1ea5t d\u1ea5u. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nghi ng\u1edd Alex \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 ra s\u00f4ng Meenachil trong \u0111\u00eam r\u1ed3i nh\u1ea3y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 t\u1eed. C\u1ea3nh s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 chia nhau n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm d\u1ecdc s\u00f4ng Meenachil. Nh\u01b0ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1i qua, t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n g\u00ec.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed v\u00ec Argentina thua th\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fan Messi t\u1ef1 t\u1eed v\u00ec Argentina thua th\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Fan-Messi-tu-tu-vi-Argentina-thua-tham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Alex c\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfc \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f3 in h\u00ecnh Messi c\u1ee7a con trai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n \u0111au b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 fan d\u00f9 ch\u1eb3ng ngh\u0129 qu\u1ea9n nh\u01b0 Alex song c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t l\u01b0\u1ee1i h\u00e1i t\u1eed th\u1ea7n trong d\u1ecbp xem World Cup. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y 14/6/2014, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p fan x\u1ea5u s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c ch\u00ecm v\u00e0o gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 ng\u00e0n thu, kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd t\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i n\u1eefa sau khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u1ee9c th\u00e2u \u0111\u00eam xem ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil. H\u1ecd qua \u0111\u1eddi v\u00ec ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, c\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a tin fan 56 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf t\u1ec9nh H\u1ed3 B\u1eafc c\u00f3 t\u00ean Zhao \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean c\u01a1n nh\u1ed3i m\u00e1u c\u01a1 tim sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ru\u1ed9t, \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c Mexico. Vi\u1ec7c xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fac mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 huy\u1ebft \u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba khi c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9, c\u00e1c k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c fan m\u1ed7i d\u1ecbp nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup hay EURO di\u1ec5n ra. H\u1ecd khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c theo d\u00f5i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n, c\u00e1c fan c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, sinh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng fan m\u1eafc v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 tim m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng fan ch\u00e2u \u00c1 hay ph\u1ea3i xem \u0111\u00eam h\u00f4m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Bongdaplus.vn<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3794","checkdouble":"189400"},{"date":"07:56 24/06","title":"Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Miura b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i t\u0103ng cao.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: start; \"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ea1i V-League</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 23/6, hai CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, TP.HCM x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 13 v\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, HLV Miura c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, HLV Miura c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/1529763926_7.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miura c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 TP.HCM c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i binh Matias Gonzalez. V\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t V-League hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1edbi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho CLB TPHCM t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5, \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb bi\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Phi S\u01a1n, Gonzalez ch\u1ea1y c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap TP.HCM thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng TP.HCM \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh \u0111\u00f2n \u2018h\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u2019 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Khi hi\u1ec7p 2 tr\u00f4i qua \u00edt ph\u00fat, CLB TP.HCM li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi H\u1eefu \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 L\u00ea S\u1ef9 Minh. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef t\u1edbi h\u1ebft 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn TP.HCM cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u1ea5y lu\u00f4n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB TP.HCM c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3793","checkdouble":"189394"},{"date":"08:02 24/06","title":"Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.</h2><h2>SLNA k\u00e9o d\u00e0i m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB SLNA \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. T\u00ednh c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/12/danh-bai-binh-duong-hlv-slna-het-loi-khen-vien-binh-tu-flc-thanh-hoa.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League, SLNA ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u00a0<span style=\"background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); color: rgb(58, 58, 58); font-family: Arial;\">Ng\u00f4 Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 44 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</span>. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, HLV SLNA \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng cho hay: \u201c\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i, t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn, s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u00f4m nay c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u1ebft. D\u00f9 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, SLNA \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u1edbi 17 \u0111i\u1ec3m. N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u1eeda tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u1ea3 quan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League-2018.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3792","checkdouble":"189395"},{"date":"08:06 24/06","title":"HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.</h2><h2>HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a TP.HCM tr\u01b0\u1edbc SLNA</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 23/6, CLB TP.HCM b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 trong hi\u1ec7p 2, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Minh Trung ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TPHCM h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TPHCM h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/1529763879_2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Miura tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Miura t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng ta ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n. \u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, CLB TP.HCM bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1ed1ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo t\u00f4i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d, HLV Miura n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, HLV V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Minh Trung c\u1ee7a TP.HCM l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh chia s\u1ebb: \u201cV\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p hai th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. T\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i sai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c TP.HCM, cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018 \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng khi Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f9ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br />\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\">Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3791","checkdouble":"189396"},{"date":"08:13 24/06","title":"Sau v\u00f2ng 15 V-League: N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/sau-vong-15-vleague-nong-cuoc-dua-tru-hang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc TP.HCM. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng n\u0103m nay th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.</h2><h2>1. N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 TP.HCM trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua 23/6, CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111u\u1ed5i k\u1ecbp hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 TP.HCM v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay c\u00e0ng th\u00eam n\u00f3ng khi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean th\u00ec SLNA v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chu\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 15 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sau v\u00f2ng 15 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i TP.HCM c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League th\u00eam k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110inh H\u1ed3ng Vinh \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 11 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 TP.HCM. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, vi\u1ec7c C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1c 2-5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Ch\u1ec9 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u00f4ng H\u00e0n hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng san b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p 1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi Ho\u00e0ng V\u0169 Samson \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 74 v\u00e0 90\u2019+3 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 5-2 t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Da Nang\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/ha-noi-vs-da-nang-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i '\u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p' ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 15 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i gia t\u0103ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm n\u1ebfu duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. HAGL c\u1eaft m\u1ea1ch th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL vs Sai Gon\" title=\"HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/05_saigon_hagl_140418_anhkhahoa06_tydi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00fap h\u1ecd l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 ghi li\u1ec1n 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ngo\u1ea1i binh Da Sylva c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 trong l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>4. V-League \u2018thi\u1ebfu nhi\u1ec7t\u2019 v\u00ec World Cup<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i V-League k\u00e9m s\u1ee9c h\u00fat m\u00f9a World Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u khi m\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ea1i tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian World Cup di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn ra \u1edf v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. CLB HAGL v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat nh\u1ea5t V-League c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 thu h\u00fat 5 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 6 v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"San Hang Day\" title=\"S\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/21/san_hang_day.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby v\u1eafng v\u1ebb t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby, s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 4 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn kho\u1ea3ng\u00a01/4 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ed9i c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng khu v\u1ef1c tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 l\u00e8o t\u00e8o m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. Sau s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 ch\u1ea3o l\u1eeda \u0111\u00f4ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a V-League khi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ea1t x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 ho\u1eb7c h\u01a1n 10.000 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 HAGL, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh,\u2026 th\u00ec s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 lu\u00f4n \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao kho\u1ea3ng 14 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.000 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3n \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00fang th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 V-League k\u00e9m s\u1ee9c h\u00fat khi m\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0 VCK World Cup 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>BXH V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh-168-189396.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-sau-khi-tphcm-xuong-bet-bang-sau-tran-thua-nam-dinh-168-189396.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi TP.HCM xu\u1ed1ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ed7i cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thang-tran-thu-3-lien-tiep-hlv-slna-noi-gi-168-189395.html\">Th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV SLNA n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV SLNA Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nam-dinh-chiec-ghe-cua-hlv-miura-bi-lung-lay-du-doi-168-189394.html\">Thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a HLV Miura b\u1ecb lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM v\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3790","checkdouble":"189397"}]}